const API_URL = 'http://localhost:8080';

export const API_ROUTES = {
  login: `${API_URL}/login`,
  signup: `${API_URL}/signup`,
  fetchUserDetails: `${API_URL}/api/fetch/user`,
  profilePic: `${API_URL}/profilePic`,
  createCheckOutSession: `${API_URL}/create-checkout-session`,
  bannersDisplay: `${API_URL}/banners`,
  getUserEventCount: `${API_URL}/getUserEvents`,
  getJoinedEventsCount: `${API_URL}/getJoinedEventsCount`,
  getRegistrationAllEventCount: `${API_URL}/getRegistrationsCount`,
  getAllEventAllAttendeeData: `${API_URL}/getEventAttendees/data`,
  getAllRegCountGraph: `${API_URL}/api/registrationCounts`
};
